                Bureaucracy fosters Extremism
                
            </title>
            <updated>2024-07-09T09:35:08Z</updated>
            <id>https://wewillwin.dev/bureaucracy-fosters-extremism/</id>
            <content type="html">
                &lt;p&gt;The less powerful you feel, the more power you seek after and the more drastic measures you think of.&lt;br /&gt;
Bureaucracy is the system by which power is subverted upwards.&lt;br /&gt;
Extremism is the system by which power is taken forcefully downwards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bureaucracy needs &lt;em&gt;order&lt;/em&gt; as one big &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;mass&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
Extremism is the &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;small&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; swing back into &lt;em&gt;disorder&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you think this is true?&lt;br /&gt;
When does it really trigger someone to act extremism out?&lt;/p&gt;

